title: New: October Tooth – Fill
body:
Beautiful artwork, beautiful songs from Tennessee’s **October Tooth**.

Really intimate sounding vocals litter Casiotone For The Painfully Alone styled programmed beats; it’s a delicate composition, deserving of your attention for it’s four minute length. Check out _Fill_ below, lifted from a self-released EP, out on [Bandcamp](http://octobertooth.bandcamp.com/releases).
